lead_paragraph: President Tayyip Erdogan's tightening grip on power is likely to meet little more than symbolic resistance from the West next year, as Turkey's G20 presidency and the fight against Islamic State trump concerns about a slide towards authoritarianism.

headline.main: In Dealings With the West, Erdogan Holds All the Cards
headline.print_headline: In Dealings With the West, Erdogan Holds All the Cards
